- Fomichyov!
- Here!

6
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:45,877
- Goryshkin!
- Here!

7
00:00:46,640 --> 00:00:48,517
- Borovsky!
- Here!

8
00:00:48,800 --> 00:00:50,119
- Kukunin!
- Here!

9
00:00:50,560 --> 00:00:52,118
- Alimov!
- Here!

10
00:00:52,400 --> 00:00:54,038
- Ryabinin!
- Here!

11
00:00:55,720 --> 00:01:00,350
The roll call of Section 2 done.
No one absent without leave.

12
00:01:00,800 --> 00:01:03,678
The roll call of Section 3 done.
No one absent without leave.

13
00:01:03,960 --> 00:01:07,032
The roll call of Section 4 done.
No one absent without leave.

14
00:01:07,320 --> 00:01:09,834
- Take them to the barracks.
- Yes, sir!

15
00:01:10,320 --> 00:01:11,309
Section!

16
00:01:11,800 --> 00:01:15,588
Left turn! Quick march!

17
00:01:16,680 --> 00:01:20,275
Ryabinin, stay behind.
Come here.

18
00:01:26,640 --> 00:01:28,517
You're lucky, your wife's here.

19
00:01:30,000 --> 00:01:31,877
- Why?
- She wants a visit with you.

20
00:01:32,160 --> 00:01:34,674
I didn't ask her to. I don't want
this visit.

21
00:01:34,920 --> 00:01:40,119
She took a train, then a plane,
then a 24-hour bumpy truck ride.

22
00:01:40,400 --> 00:01:41,879
I don't care, I'm not going.

23
00:01:42,160 --> 00:01:44,594
You will go without convoy.
I trust you.

24
00:01:45,080 --> 00:01:46,354
Where to?

25
00:01:46,640 --> 00:01:50,110
She's taken a room in the village.
Here, the address.

26
00:01:50,400 --> 00:01:52,277
You drop by Ivan Gerasimovich

27
00:01:53,160 --> 00:01:55,355
and pick up the accordion he fixed.

28
00:01:55,800 --> 00:01:59,873
You're a musician, this is your
department. Check if he fixed it right.

29
00:02:00,160 --> 00:02:02,037
- Yes, sir.
- That's better.

30
00:02:02,320 --> 00:02:07,030
You can't refuse to go
to pick up the accordion.

31
00:02:07,800 --> 00:02:11,031
But mind you, Ryabinin,
at 8 sharp you are to stand in line.

32
00:02:11,480 --> 00:02:17,430
Your leave is until the morning roll
call. Tardiness will mean an escape.

33
00:03:00,720 --> 00:03:02,199
How far is the village?

34
00:03:02,480 --> 00:03:04,869
Not far, about nine or ten kilometers.

35
00:03:05,160 --> 00:03:08,596
And don't think of bringing in booze,
a knife or money. I'll find it anyway.

36
00:03:08,920 --> 00:03:10,353
I know.

37
00:03:13,920 --> 00:03:17,435
Your pass is good until 8 a.m.
Be here on the dot.

38
00:03:17,720 --> 00:03:21,190
If you're late, it'll mean an escape.
You'll do an additional time. Go!

